xyz.swatt.data_mapping_validator

Class LongMappingValidator

  • java.lang.Object
    • xyz.swatt.data_mapping_validator.AbstractDataMapping<java.lang.Long>
      • xyz.swatt.data_mapping_validator.LongMappingValidator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataMappingValidator<java.lang.Long> 

    @LogMethods
public class LongMappingValidator
extends AbstractDataMapping<java.lang.Long>

    Use this class to validate that 2 different Longs, Integers, or Shorts are equivalent.

    Note: This class is used instead of direct comparison, to simplify large batches of comparisons.

    Author:
    Brandon Dudek (BrandonDudek)
